# UI Rules — obm_gen_with_ai

> Variables: See `_project_config.mdc`. Key values: `{{BRAND}}`, `{{TEXT_DEFAULT}}`, `{{TEXT_GREY}}`, `{{TEXT_LIGHT_GREY}}`, `{{DIVIDER}}`, `{{SUCCESS}}`, `{{WARNING}}`, `{{ERROR}}`, `{{BG_LIGHT}}`, `{{BG_CARD}}`, `{{TEXT_STYLE_CLASS}}`, `{{TEXT_COMMON}}`, `{{TEXT_FOCUS}}`, `{{TEXT_LABEL}}`, `{{TEXT_LABEL_REQUIRED}}`, `{{TEXT_FIELD}}`, `{{TEXT_ERROR}}`, `{{TEXT_DISABLE}}`, `{{TEXT_HINT}}`, `{{TEXT_WIDGET}}`, `{{SVG_HELPER}}`, `{{M_SHOW_DIALOG}}`, `{{M_SHOW_TOAST}}`, `{{DIALOG_TYPE_ENUM}}`, `{{DIALOG_TYPES}}`, `{{TOAST_TYPE_ENUM}}`, `{{TOAST_TYPES}}`, `{{I18N_CLASS}}`, `{{I18N_GETTER}}`, `{{FONT}}`.

## NEVER (Hard Rules)

| # | NEVER DO                               | INSTEAD USE                          |
|---|----------------------------------------|--------------------------------------|
| 1 | Hardcode hex color outside `ColorApp`  | `{{BRAND}}`, `{{TEXT_DEFAULT}}`, etc. |
| 2 | Inline `TextStyle(...)` in widgets     | `{{TEXT_STYLE_CLASS}}.*` / `{{TEXT_WIDGET}}(...)` |
| 3 | Hardcode display strings               | `{{I18N_GETTER}}`                    |
| 4 | SVG via `SvgPicture.asset` directly    | `{{SVG_HELPER}}(...)`                |
| 5 | Call `showDialog`/`showToast` from widget | `provider.{{M_SHOW_DIALOG}}/{{M_SHOW_TOAST}}` (via eventStream) |
| 6 | Wrap body with extra loading overlay    | `{{CONSUMER_BASE}}` handles loading state  |
| 7 | Use barrel import `package:obm_gen_with_ai/core/` (file does not exist) | Import directly from sub-paths |

