## Dialogs — Triggered from Provider

```dart
// WRONG — called directly from widget
showDialog(context: context, builder: (_) => AlertDialog(...));

// CORRECT — dispatched via eventStream
provider.{{M_SHOW_DIALOG}}(
  type: {{DIALOG_TYPE_ENUM}}.success,
  title: {{I18N_CLASS}}.notification,
  content: {{I18N_CLASS}}.downloadDataSuccess,
  onActionCallback: (action) {
    if (action == DialogActionType.confirm) { ... }
  },
);
```

